text: ABCC can mean: * Atomic Bomb Casualty Commission * Angami Baptist Church Council * Arunachal Baptist Church Council * Australian Building and Construction Commission, a current Australian Government agency (that has existed since 2016) * Office of the Australian Building and Construction Commissioner, a former Australian Government agency that existed from 2005 to 2012 * The Association of British Chambers of Commerce, since 1996 known as the British Chambers of Commerce
title: ABCC
